ğŸŒ Djangoâ€™da WSGI va ASGI nima?

Django â€” bu web-framework, yaâ€™ni u brauzerdan keladigan so'rovlarni (HTTP request) qabul qilib, javob (response) qaytaradi. Lekin Django o'zi buni to'g'ridan-to'g'ri qilolmaydi â€” bu ishni server interfeysi degan narsa bajaradi.
ğŸ¤” WSGI va ASGI nima?
Texnologiya	To'liq nomi	Tavsif	Django versiyasi
ğŸ§© WSGI	Web Server Gateway Interface	Sinxron ishlaydi. Har bir so'rov alohida process/threadda ishlaydi	Django 3.0 gacha (asosiy)
âš¡ ASGI	Asynchronous Server Gateway Interface	Asinxron ishlaydi. Bir vaqtning o'zida ko'plab so'rovlarni bajaradi	Django 3.0 dan boshlab
ğŸ” Qachon qaysi interfeysdan foydalanish kerak?

    WSGI: Oddiy web saytlar, bloglar, ma'lumotnomalar

    ASGI: Real-time ilovalar (chat, yangiliklar oqimi), WebSockets, ko'p sonli bir vaqtli foydalanuvchilar

ğŸ“Š Django Models - Ma'lumotlar Bazasi bilan Ishlash
ğŸ—ï¸ Model Yaratish
python

from django.db import models

class Student(models.Model):
    name = models.CharField(max_length=100)
    age = models.IntegerField()
    grade = models.CharField(max_length=10)

    def __str__(self):
        return self.name

ğŸ’¾ CRUD Operatsiyalari
1. Ma'lumot qo'shish - save()
python

student = Student(name="Ali", age=16, grade="10A")
student.save()

2. Barcha ma'lumotlarni olish - objects.all()
python

students = Student.objects.all()

3. Filtrlash - objects.filter() (WHERE sharti)
python

ten_b_students = Student.objects.filter(grade="10B")

4. Bitta yozuvni olish - objects.get()
python

student = Student.objects.get(id=1)

5. Shartga mos bo'lmaganlarni olish - objects.exclude()
python

not_10b = Student.objects.exclude(grade="10B")

6. Tartiblash - objects.order_by()
python

students = Student.objects.order_by("age")        # o'sish tartibida
students = Student.objects.order_by("-age")       # kamayish tartibida

7. Soni - count()
python

student_count = Student.objects.count()

8. Yangilash - update()
python

Student.objects.filter(grade="10A").update(grade="11A")

9. O'chirish - delete()
python

Student.objects.get(id=3).delete()

10. Ma'lumotlarni formatda olish
python

# Lug'at formatida
Student.objects.values("name", "grade")

# Ro'yxat formatida
Student.objects.values_list("name", flat=True)

